name: Delete Duplicate Data
author: Bhagirath

sections.description:
Delete Duplicate Post, Page, Attachment and Custom Post by just one Click.

You can delete following duplicate data.

  • Post
  • Page
  • Custom Post
  • Attachment
  • Category
  • Taxonomy
  • Custom Category

You can delete duplicate data Permanently or move to trash.

In Future We Will Add Schedule Deletion that can be very usefully with auto blogging.
sections.installation:
1. Upload plugin-name.php to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
